        <title>桂林山水甲天下，玉碧罗青意可参</title>
        <link>https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/</link>
        <pubDate>Fri, 04 May 2012 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120429_095040-Large.jpg" alt="Featured image of post 桂林山水甲天下，玉碧罗青意可参" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3548-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3548-Medium_hub56276c96d95f4b0ca1c00c19046cee6_182396_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3548-Medium_hub56276c96d95f4b0ca1c00c19046cee6_182396_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“桂林山水甲天下”，如此名气，如此牛逼之描述，对于吾等屁国小民来说，神往久矣。此七字，出于寡人右上方石壁碑刻，若放大之，则为下图光景，为乡贡进士张次良所作。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; 石刻不可不谓桂林之一大瑰宝，此有独秀峰之石刻，又有龙隐岩等众多古人之乱涂乱画作品，虽然不乏号称国家NX级珍贵文物，但乱砸乱凿弄疼了石头总是不好的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120430_124832-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120430_124832-Medium_hu199fff82580139c1ff6fbfe19d4d604a_216356_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120430_124832-Medium_hu199fff82580139c1ff6fbfe19d4d604a_216356_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; 说到石头不得不提的就是石头山了，好吧，你桂林山水甲天下，好歹是以山和水为冠的，那总的有座像样的山，有滩没臭味的水给人看吧。可，山是啥？山就是石头！妹的，坑爹呢。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120429_164057.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;3056&#34;
	height=&#34;944&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120429_164057_hu7890cb56aa3fbd5ba0a8d65a6b8c085d_504018_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120429_164057_hu7890cb56aa3fbd5ba0a8d65a6b8c085d_504018_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;323&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;776px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;无心吐槽，石头就算了，堆那么高，说它是山也不过分。但一定要说这群石头山就能扛下全中国其他名山大岳，还真感觉有点忤逆不道呀。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;石头完了就是水了。漓江呀，洒下过俺几升液体排泄物的地方（沃勒个擦的，后来才知道佛山的自来水水源为河水，就是漓江下游啊），也是各种污水管废水管的收集器，不见得保护得多么好呀，只不过是因为再上游真心没啥工业企业了，污染得不多而已。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120429_095040-Large.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1920&#34;
	height=&#34;563&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120429_095040-Large_hu2ade7d8fe8d7ff3f7acc5c05b7508f8b_123293_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120429_095040-Large_hu2ade7d8fe8d7ff3f7acc5c05b7508f8b_123293_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;341&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;818px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;本来吧，山和水结合起来能有上图这个水平，我也就不准备再说啥了。但泥马哥风风火火不远千里跑来桂林，第一眼见到漓江时居然丫的看到的是这货，不禁得虎躯一震，鬼子当年打桂林真心没打够呀？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/1335956620101-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/1335956620101-Medium_hu44c6d9a46e40342cae64737fde43f72f_84475_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/1335956620101-Medium_hu44c6d9a46e40342cae64737fde43f72f_84475_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;说到日本娃，不得不提到下面这三位了：阚维雍（131师师长）、陈济桓（桂林城防司令部参谋长）、吕旃蒙（第31军参谋长）。但似乎再多说啥也没什么用，猴子为伴略见一斑。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120430_112400-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;576&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120430_112400-Medium_hufceb5a884165bdfdd0d6b7569b5631f4_124828_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120430_112400-Medium_hufceb5a884165bdfdd0d6b7569b5631f4_124828_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;75&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;180px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不知道AAAA级景区到底是个啥概念，只知道，随便市内公园啥的都是AAAA级景区，还都TM比京城那几堵墙的门票还贵。下面图中，就左上角那一撮小山，约莫几亩地的面积，居然也是个AAAA，沃勒割草，这TM评级机关当年收了多少钱啊？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3577-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3577-Medium_huaec398e9b25f59ea6fc00609998e80a7_163454_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3577-Medium_huaec398e9b25f59ea6fc00609998e80a7_163454_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;好吧，我承认孤陋寡闻了，去了桂林才知道，阳朔才是丫桂林最牛叉的地方，据说阳朔山水冠桂林，坑爹的宣传。于是风尘仆仆的赶到阳朔来围观一下，本来没报多大期望，结果却是也就那么点小期待被实现了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120502_131742-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120502_131742-Medium_hueeee945f8353aadc98a55a82b89048f2_73388_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120502_131742-Medium_hueeee945f8353aadc98a55a82b89048f2_73388_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;无语，给我活生生的来了一场暴雨游漓江的大戏。船家大叔，美其名曰“烟雨漓江”，好吧，暴雨蒙蒙啥都看不到的漓江，估计这辈子也没机会再见第二次了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120502_151201-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120502_151201-Medium_hua43f566906eb54662e28d5a3516a3f46_220379_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120502_151201-Medium_hua43f566906eb54662e28d5a3516a3f46_220379_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这就是阳朔最牛叉的西街了，如果把后边的石头给PS掉，说这地方是湘西凤凰，估计没人会觉得有异常。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;山顶上太阳射得厉害，亮瞎了俺双5.3视力的钛合金狗眼&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3352-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3352-Medium_hu7c526b7fbde11b02d822be582ba861c0_96035_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3352-Medium_hu7c526b7fbde11b02d822be582ba861c0_96035_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;一对好G友，攻受对比明显，都搞大肚子了&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120501_104718-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120501_104718-Medium_hu0e2cbf690c19970809b9dff4e14a1a3e_206175_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/20120501_104718-Medium_hu0e2cbf690c19970809b9dff4e14a1a3e_206175_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;213青年欢乐多，谁TM说这后面是骆驼了&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3409-Medium.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3409-Medium_hu4187a392debfd9f4648606126abf0e77_152464_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2012-05-04-guilin/images/IMG_3409-Medium_hu4187a392debfd9f4648606126abf0e77_152464_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
